		{
			description: [
				"&eAscension Megamons&r are powerful, oversized Cobblemon that roam specific biomes and dimensions. They're visually distinct — larger models, visible auras, unmistakable presence."
				""
				"Your first task is just to find one and observe it safely. Don't engage. Study it from a distance."
				""
				"Note its type, the biome it's in, and how it moves. Every piece of information helps. You'll be fighting it soon enough."
				""
				"&7Tip: Megamons have larger models and a visible aura — study them carefully before rushing in.&r"
			]
			icon: "cobblemon:ultra_ball"
			id: "10000000000000A3"
			min_width: 330
			rewards: [{
				count: 3
				id: "10000000000000A2"
