		{
			dependencies: ["10000000000000A3"]
			description: [
				"Before you fight, know what you're dealing with. Identify the Megamon's type and approximate level from a safe distance."
				""
				"Type determines which of your Cobblemon have the advantage. Level tells you whether your current team is ready or whether you need to grind more before engaging."
				""
				"Use the Cobblepedia to look up the species once you've identified it. Read the entry. Plan your counter team. Preparation is the difference between a clean win and a wipe."
				""
				"&7Tip: Use Cobblepedia to look up the species and plan your counter team in advance.&r"
			]
			id: "10000000000000A6"
			min_width: 330
			rewards: [{
				count: 2
				id: "10000000000000A5"
