		{
			dependencies: ["10000000000000A9"]
			description: [
				"Now win."
				""
				"Megamons are designed to be difficult. High HP, strong moves, and the ability to outlast a poorly prepared team. Status conditions are your best tool — paralysis slows them down, sleep buys you turns, poison chips away at their health."
				""
				"Apply a status early when their HP is still high, then grind them down. Don't try to brute force it unless your team is significantly overlevelled."
				""
				"&7Tip: Status conditions are critical against high-HP Megamons — apply them as early as possible.&r"
			]
			id: "10000000000000AC"
			min_width: 320
			rewards: [{
				count: 5
				id: "10000000000000AB"
				item: "cobblemon:ultra_ball"
				type: "item"
			}]
			shape: "hexagon"
			subtitle: "Against All Odds"
			tasks: [{
