		{
			dependencies: ["10000000000000AC"]
			description: [
				"Defeating a Megamon is impressive. Catching one is a different challenge entirely."
				""
				"Ultra Balls at low HP give the best odds, but if the fight is going long, switch to a &eTimer Ball&r — its catch rate improves the longer the battle drags on. Stalling is a legitimate strategy here."
				""
				"Reducing a Megamon to low HP without knocking it out requires precision. Bring moves that do fixed damage or have multiple weak hits rather than single powerful strikes."
				""
				"&7Tip: Timer Balls improve with every turn the battle continues — stall to maximise your odds.&r"
			]
