			description: [
				"Three different Megamon species. Each one a different fight, a different biome, a different challenge."
				""
				"Megamons don't all share territory. Some appear in specific overworld biomes, others in modded dimensions — the Aether, the Nether, or elsewhere. Your exploration skills from Chapter 3 come back into play here."
				""
				"Build your collection. A Megamon that's caught and levelled becomes one of the strongest tools in your late-game team."
				""
				"&7Tip: Explore all biomes and dimensions — Megamons don't share territory.&r"
